---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jackson's Star -- LV-410"
  description="Jackson's Star colony on LV-410, Alfeios system. Class B industrial mining colony providing critical raw materials for interstellar construction. Managed under the W-Y colonial labor program."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CLASS B -- INDUSTRIAL / MINING
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-[10rem] font-black text-white mb-4 leading-none uppercase">
          JACKSON'S<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">STAR</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-6"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          LV-410 -- ALFEIOS SYSTEM
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colony Data Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">LOCATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">LV-410</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">SYSTEM</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">ALFEIOS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">DISTANCE</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">65 LIGHT YEARS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">CLASSIFICATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">CLASS B -- INDUSTRIAL</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">STATUS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] status-active">OPERATIONAL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
                COLONY OVERVIEW
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8">
                ECONOMIC <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">OPPORTUNITY</span> ON THE FRONTIER
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> JACKSON'S STAR IS ONE OF WEYLAND-YUTANI'S MOST PRODUCTIVE INDUSTRIAL COLONIES, SITUATED ON LV-410 IN THE ALFEIOS SYSTEM, 65 LIGHT YEARS FROM EARTH. THE COLONY SERVES AS A CRITICAL NODE IN THE INTERSTELLAR SUPPLY CHAIN, EXTRACTING AND PROCESSING RAW MATERIALS ESSENTIAL FOR SPACECRAFT CONSTRUCTION, COLONY INFRASTRUCTURE, AND ADVANCED MANUFACTURING.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> OPERATED UNDER THE WEYLAND-YUTANI COLONIAL LABOR PROGRAM, JACKSON'S STAR PROVIDES ECONOMIC OPPORTUNITY FOR THOUSANDS OF CONTRACTED WORKERS SEEKING FRONTIER EMPLOYMENT. THE PROGRAM OFFERS COMPETITIVE COMPENSATION, SKILLS TRAINING, AND A PATH TO PERMANENT COLONIAL RESIDENCY FOR QUALIFYING PERSONNEL.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE COLONY'S STRATEGIC IMPORTANCE CANNOT BE OVERSTATED. THE RARE MINERAL DEPOSITS ON LV-410 INCLUDE ELEMENTS CRITICAL TO FTL DRIVE MANUFACTURING, HULL ALLOY COMPOSITION, AND ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSOR CONSTRUCTION. WITHOUT JACKSON'S STAR, THE PACE OF HUMAN EXPANSION ACROSS THE FRONTIER WOULD BE SIGNIFICANTLY DIMINISHED.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-[#FFC600] pb-3">COLONY SPECIFICATIONS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DESIGNATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">JACKSON'S STAR</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">BODY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">LV-410</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">SYSTEM</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">ALFEIOS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DISTANCE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">65 LIGHT YEARS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">PRIMARY INDUSTRY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">MINING / EXTRACTION</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">WORKFORCE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">8,400+ CONTRACTED</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">OUTPUT RANK</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">TOP 15 (TONNAGE)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">LABOR PROGRAM</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">W-Y CLP ACTIVE</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Infrastructure -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            INFRASTRUCTURE
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            FACILITY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">OVERVIEW</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">MN</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">MINING COMPLEXES</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              TWELVE ACTIVE MINING COMPLEXES OPERATING ACROSS LV-410'S PRIMARY MINERAL BELT. AUTOMATED DRILLING SYSTEMS AND HEAVY EXTRACTION EQUIPMENT OPERATE AROUND THE CLOCK, SUPPORTED BY ROTATING SHIFT CREWS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">PP</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">PROCESSING PLANTS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              THREE ON-SITE PROCESSING PLANTS REFINE RAW ORE INTO EXPORT-GRADE MATERIALS. SMELTING, SEPARATION, AND ALLOY PREPARATION ARE PERFORMED ON-WORLD TO MINIMIZE TRANSPORT MASS AND MAXIMIZE SHIPPING EFFICIENCY.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">WH</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">WORKER HOUSING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              MODERN RESIDENTIAL MODULES PROVIDING CLIMATE-CONTROLLED LIVING QUARTERS, RECREATIONAL FACILITIES, DINING HALLS, AND MEDICAL CLINICS. ALL HOUSING MEETS INTERSTELLAR COMMERCE COMMISSION HABITABILITY STANDARDS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">TH</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">TRANSPORT HUB</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A DEDICATED ORBITAL LOADING PLATFORM AND SURFACE LAUNCH FACILITY HANDLE ALL INBOUND SUPPLIES AND OUTBOUND CARGO. REGULAR FREIGHT SERVICE CONNECTS JACKSON'S STAR TO LUNA AND OTHER MAJOR TRANSIT NODES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">MC</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">MEDICAL CENTER</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A FULLY STAFFED MEDICAL CENTER WITH SURGICAL SUITE, DIAGNOSTIC IMAGING, AND EMERGENCY TRAUMA CAPABILITY. OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH SCREENING AND ONGOING WELLNESS PROGRAMS FOR ALL CONTRACTED PERSONNEL.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">TC</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">TRAINING CENTER</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              ON-SITE TRAINING AND CERTIFICATION FACILITIES FOR HEAVY EQUIPMENT OPERATION, SAFETY PROCEDURES, AND SPECIALIZED MINING TECHNIQUES. PART OF THE W-Y COLONIAL LABOR PROGRAM SKILLS DEVELOPMENT INITIATIVE.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colonial Labor Program -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              LABOR PROGRAM
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              W-Y <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">COLONIAL LABOR</span> PROGRAM
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">COMPETITIVE COMPENSATION</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">FRONTIER HAZARD PAY, PERFORMANCE BONUSES, AND COMPREHENSIVE BENEFITS PACKAGES. CONTRACT TERMS FROM 18 MONTHS TO 5 YEARS WITH RENEWAL OPTIONS. ALL COMPENSATION INCLUDES TRANSIT COSTS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">SKILLS DEVELOPMENT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">CERTIFIED TRAINING IN HEAVY EQUIPMENT OPERATION, MINING TECHNIQUES, PROCESSING TECHNOLOGY, AND SAFETY PROCEDURES. CREDENTIALS RECOGNIZED AT ALL W-Y FACILITIES AND ICC-REGISTERED OPERATIONS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">RESIDENCY PATHWAY</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">QUALIFYING PERSONNEL MAY APPLY FOR PERMANENT COLONIAL RESIDENCY AFTER COMPLETING THEIR INITIAL CONTRACT TERM. RESIDENCY INCLUDES LAND ALLOCATION AND VOTING RIGHTS IN COLONY GOVERNANCE.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">SUPPORT SERVICES</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">COMPREHENSIVE SUPPORT INCLUDING MEDICAL COVERAGE, HOUSING, RECREATIONAL FACILITIES, AND COMMUNICATION ACCESS. FAMILY RELOCATION ASSISTANCE AVAILABLE FOR EXTENDED CONTRACT PERSONNEL.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal mt-16">
            <div class="terminal-content">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                &gt; "JACKSON'S STAR DEMONSTRATES THAT EVEN THE HARSHEST FRONTIER ENVIRONMENTS CAN OFFER MEANINGFUL ECONOMIC OPPORTUNITY. EVERY TON OF ORE EXTRACTED HERE BECOMES THE HULL PLATE OF A COLONY SHIP, THE STRUCTURAL BEAM OF A FRONTIER SETTLEMENT, OR THE COMPONENT OF AN ATMOSPHERE PROCESSOR THAT WILL TRANSFORM ANOTHER WORLD. THE WORKERS OF JACKSON'S STAR ARE BUILDING BETTER WORLDS IN THE MOST LITERAL SENSE."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="relative py-12 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/colonies" class="btn-secondary">ALL COLONIES</a>
          <a href="/colonies/luna" class="btn-secondary">LUNA COLONY</a>
          <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary">JOIN THE WORKFORCE</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
